Wheeljack-X::

"He'll be fine," Jackie assures her, walking over to Blackfang and 
popping out a med-scanner from his wrist.  "A little magnetic field 
never hurt anyone.  He might have some trouble with short-term memory, 
but nothing permanent.  Now, what the slaggin' hell is wrong with this 
guy's logic circuits, to make him attack us like that?"
